DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Music & Dance\\n\\nRepresentatives from the Philharmo
 nic Society will be visiting to give a performance and share some informa
 tion on how strings\, woodwinds\, brass\, and percussion create beautiful
  music. It’s a fun\, informative way for kids (and also grown-ups) to l
 earn about various instruments.\nTIME: 11 AM Included in museum admission.
  Space is limited! Book your tickets now. \n*Members do not require a
  reservation.\n*Events and dates are subject to change.\\n\\nMore info: ht
 tps://www.pretendcity.org/events/meet-the-instrument-2/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/meet-the-instrument-2/
