UID:c41a16a47e8033d659d2bf5a7728413f@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nAges: 0-6
 0 months\\nCategory: Music & Dance\\n\\nGet ready to rock\, roll\, sway\, 
 sing\, and bop! Because we’re bringing back Kidstock Music &amp\; Arts F
 estival! Enjoy live musical performances throughout the week and explore a
  mix of musical styles! Because of your generosity during Igniting Potenti
 al\, Kidstock will be bigger\, brighter\, and more hands-on than ever!\n3/
 31\n\n11 am: The Rhythm Child Network\n2:30 pm: Pacific Dance\n\n\n4/1\n\n
 11 am: Ashley Mills Monaghan\n2:30 pm: Jukie Davie\n\n\n4/2\n\n11 am &amp\
 ; 2:30 pm DrumatiX\n\n\n4/3\n\n11 am: Conga Kids\n2:30 pm: Philharmonic So
 ciety’s Orange County Youth Symphony musicians\n\n\n4/4\n\n11 am: SoCal 
 Drum Party\n1 pm: Bhangra by Nature\n\n4/5 CLOSED for Easter\nWeek 2\n4/7\
 n\n11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm Fouta Toro West African Dance and Drum Ensemble\n\
 n4/8\n\n11 am: Backhaus Dance\n2:30 pm: Mommy Center Music\n\n4/9\n\n11 am
 : WeBreak Hip-Hop Dance Company\n2:30 pm: Ufirst Artist\n\n4/10\n\n11 am &
 amp\; 2:30 pm: Platinum Performing Arts\n\n4/11\n\n11 am: El Centro Cultur
 al de México\n1 pm: The Portobellas\n2:30 pm: Kymberly Stewart\n\nThis ex
 hibit is included in museum admission. Space is limited! Book your tick
 ets now. \nEvent DetailsMarch 31 – April 11Performance times vary by da
 ySpring Break hours: Tuesday–Sunday\, 10 am–4 pmClosed April 5 for Eas
 terEvents subject to change.\nFAQs\nIs Kidstock included with admission?Ye
 s. All performances are included with regular museum admission.\nWhat ages
  is Kidstock best for?The festival is designed for children ages 0–8 and
  their families.\nDo performances happen every day?Yes. Live music or danc
 e performances take place daily during the festival\, except when the muse
 um is closed.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock/
