 pmental milestones and receive valuable insights into their growth\n⦁ Vi
 sion Screenings: Detect early signs of vision issues to ensure your child
 ’s eyes are healthy.\n⦁ Dental Screenings: Keep your child’s smile b
 right and healthy with a free dental check-up.\n⦁ Social-Emotional Scree
 nings: Assess your child’s emotional well-being and get support for the
 ir mental health.\n⦁ And more!\nWhy Attend?\nEarly Detection: Catch pote
 ntial health concerns early\, allowing for timely intervention and support
 .\nFree Services: Access these important health screenings at no cost to y
 ou.\nExpert Guidance: Receive advice and resources from trained profession
 als to support your child’s development and health.\nPLUS\, your child c
 an earn a FREE ticket to Pretend City by completing 3 Health screenings!\n
